{
  "stem": "14897.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So for those few days, of course, they searched the entire perimeter, where we were not allowed to be.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And after that, they exterminated whoever stayed in that section who had not been able to come out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they felt it was a more efficient way of handling things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my mother and I managed to get out because of being friends with this Mr.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Rowinski, who in turn was sort of friends with Schultz, the owner, at the time, of that factory.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they gave us some papers and allowed us to march out with the contingent from that factory.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my father was with us, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we marched out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And by this point-- at that point, the only places where you were allowed to live was in the buildings adjacent to the factories.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So now you didn't have one ghetto, but you had several tiny little ghettos.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you were never allowed in the street, and you were-- except when you marched out with the whole group to work from one building to the next.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But, of course, my mother and I did not have work at that factory, so we were, again, wild in that building next to the-- to the factory.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we could see that there was no good end for us all to this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in that factory, there were also Polish people working who came into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father was acquainted with them and negotiated with one gentleman by the name of Mr.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Rozwadowski, R-O-Z-W-A-D-O-W-S-K-I, who had two aunts living in a little town near Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Very nice people, all of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And his aunts needed a little income, but they didn't want to fleece anybody.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They did want to help.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
